item.description:
bucket 策略配置 以下例子存储桶名称为pic，将 pic 设置为只读。
{ &#34;Version&#34;: &#34;2012-10-17&#34;, &#34;Statement&#34;: [ { &#34;Effect&#34;: &#34;Allow&#34;, &#34;Principal&#34;: { &#34;AWS&#34;: [ &#34;*&#34; ] }, &#34;Action&#34;: [ &#34;s3:GetObject&#34; ], &#34;Resource&#34;: [ &#34;arn:aws:s3:::pic/**&#34; ] } ] } access token 策略设置 access token 拥有读写权限。
{ &#34;Version&#34;: &#34;2012-10-17&#34;, &#34;Statement&#34;: [ { &#34;Effect&#34;: &#34;Allow&#34;, &#34;Action&#34;: [ &#34;s3:GetBucketLocation&#34;, &#34;s3:ListBucket&#34; ], &#34;Resource&#34;: [ &#34;arn:aws:s3:::pic&#34; ] }, { &#34;Effect&#34;: &#34;Allow&#34;, &#34;Action&#34;: [ &#34;s3:GetObject&#34;, &#34;s3:PutObject&#34; ], &#34;Resource&#34;: [ &#34;arn:aws:s3:::pic/*&#34; ] } ] }
